name: Popis looking at her mom
description: This photography was taken on May 13th 2021. Here we can see Popis looking at her mom JessyTsuki. Popis is a female cat found starving and almost dying on the streets of Santiago de Chile, by buying this NFT you will help us raise her as she deserves, we'll use 100% of the funds to buy food, vaccines and her overall health expenses, in return we'll be updating you about her status by updating photos and videos on her social networks! Thanks for helping us and greetings from Chile <3
